casebody.data:
STATE of Missouri, Respondent,
v.
Ashley Nicole PHILLIPS, Appellant. WD 80049 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: SEPTEMBER 25, 2018 Robert J Bartholomew, Jr., Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Christian Lehmberg, Columbia, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Before Division Three: Anthony Rex Gabbert, Presiding Judge, Victor C. Howard, Judge, Alok Ahuja, Judge

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Ashley N. Phillips appeals from a judgment entered upon a jury verdict convicting her of the class B felony of robbery in the second degree pursuant to Section 569.030, RSMo 2000. We affirm. Rule 30.25(b).
